function [fitresult, gof] = Sine(Length, Capacity_voltage_mv)
%CREATEFIT(LENGTH,CAPACITY_VOLTAGE_MV)
%  Create a fit.
%
%  Data for 'sine fit' fit:
%      X Input: Length
%      Y Output: Capacity_voltage_mv
%  Output:
